data.description: Welcome to 143 Spring Street! This nicely recently renovated home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 1,340 Sq Ft of living space! Charming front covered porch that is the perfect spot to enjoy your morning cup of coffee! Upon entry you will notice the bright open floor plan with beautiful LVP flooring throughout and updated light fixtures. The spacious living room opens into the gorgeous kitchen which offers stainless steel appliances, granite counters, subway tile backsplash and a great sized dining area. The primary owners bedroom is spacious and offer with an en-suite renovated luxury bathroom with a beautiful walk-in shower. There are also two additional bedrooms with access to the renovated hall bathroom.
